Campbell Printing Press & Manuf’g Co. v. Sidebotham. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 31, 1892.) Action by the Campbell Printing Press Manufacturing Company against Thomas B. Sidebotham, Jr.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and O’Brien and Ingraham, JJ.

No opinion. Upon payment by appellant of $10 costs, motion denied.
